        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Some very usefull enhancements for Zend_Db.\n\nZend_Db functionality for working with table structure.\n\nPossible interface:\n{code}\n$table = new Table(); \/\/ extends Zend_Db_Table\n\n$table->deleteField(\n\ttitle \/\/ field title in DB\n);\n\n$table->addField(\n\ttitle, \/\/ field title in DB\n\t'VARCHAR', \/\/type\n\t255, \/\/ length\n\tnull, \/\/ default value\n\t...\n);\n\n$table->alterField(\n\ttitle, \/\/ field title in DB\n\t'VARCHAR', \/\/type\n\t255, \/\/ length\n\tnull, \/\/ default value\n\t...\n);\n{code}\n\nFunctionality for table structure import into DB and export to xml or other format would be very usefull too.\n\nPossible interface:\n{code}\n$table = new Table(); \/\/ extends Zend_Db_Table\n\n$table->importStructure('table_structure.xml');\n\n$table->exportStructure('table_structure.xml');\n\n{code}\n"
        },
